WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.001 --> 00:00:02.903
It is Cyber Monday,
the online shopping day

00:00:02.936 --> 00:00:05.239
where you can throw away
all the money you saved

00:00:05.272 --> 00:00:06.840
at the stores on Black Friday!

00:00:06.874 --> 00:00:09.243
And congratulations, by the way,
to those of you who survived

00:00:09.276 --> 00:00:12.546
Black Friday, that capitalist
spectacle where shoppers

00:00:12.579 --> 00:00:15.115
from all walks of life come
together to spread holiday cheer

00:00:15.148 --> 00:00:17.050
and punch their fellow man
in the (bleep) face

00:00:17.084 --> 00:00:18.685
for a kid's toy.

00:00:18.719 --> 00:00:20.754
