-Whoa! Whoa! Whoa!
-(indistinct shouting)

00:00:28.195 --> 00:00:30.564
(sighing):
Oh!

00:00:30.597 --> 00:00:33.066
Wow. Look at those savings.

00:00:33.100 --> 00:00:34.768
His life is half off!

00:00:34.801 --> 00:00:36.537
(laughter)

00:00:36.570 --> 00:00:38.038
