-(applause)

00:00:38.071 --> 00:00:42.075
Hey, no. Stop it, Pete. Stop it.

00:00:42.109 --> 00:00:44.711
-Uh... these...
-(laughter)

00:00:44.745 --> 00:00:47.681
These poor S.O.B.s
trampling one another

00:00:47.714 --> 00:00:50.217
like spooked buffalo
to get a deal on

00:00:50.250 --> 00:00:51.618
electronic Panini makers.

00:00:51.652 --> 00:00:53.353
This is an American tradition,
you guys.

00:00:53.387 --> 00:00:55.422
But what about our neighbors
to the north?

00:00:55.455 --> 00:00:57.624
Check out this video posted
by Suzette Belliveau.

00:00:57.658 --> 00:01:00.627
